result.name: Lan Fong Yuen

reviews.text: 24 May 19: very good taste, very responsive service, the toast is the best in town even better than 澳洲牛奶公司. The tea is ok, the tomato soup macaroni is good, I love the home-made style soup rather than instant tomato soup. Overall is good except the price is a bit high for a breakfast. Will come again and try their BBQ pork.

Classic HK-style "chaan teng" serving milk tea, toast with sweetened condensed milk, noodles, etc. The venue is reminiscent of yesteryear, with green and white tiles and old pictures of famous HK singers. For such a famous place, the food and drink quality (surprisingly) left something to be desired, but the overall experience was enjoyable.
Just a regular local restaurant, even the milk tea is pretty average, totally not as good as the original one in central, the seats are a lot more comfortable tho
Attitude is okay for us. Food is average. Milk tea is good but the chicken noodle with spring union is just average costing hkd52, not a fair deal personally.
Milk tea is good, but the price in average is on high side.

reviews.text: 凍奶茶表現太不好了👎
午餐肉很難吃😔😔😔
凍奶茶都是冰塊😑CP值太差了
老字號;出名絲襪奶茶兼上了很多次的優異獎在國際旅遊書。所以現在搬到港澳碼頭;不防一試。
第一天剛下船本來想吃的但客人多到誇張所以當時放棄，不過星期日下午再去反而沒有什麼人，鹹檸七很特別，整體沒有難吃，一開始是想到本店但沒開所以來到碼頭這邊
